snippet.title: Bulletstorm VR - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase Winter 2023
snippet.description: Bulletstorm VR's latest trailer showcases the ability to play as Trishka, features two new levels, and a new blade weapon to the action shooter game. Bulletstorm VR puts you in the boots of Grayson Hunt, elite assassin and squad leader, as he battles his way across a hostile world in Virtual Reality. Bulletstorm VR will be available on PlayStation 5, PlayStation VR2, PC, and Meta Quest on January 18, 2024.
